<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="iddd20efaf-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06" identifier="/us/usc/t12/s4406"><num value="4406">§ 4406.</num><heading> Relationship to other payments systems</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">This chapter shall have no effect by implication or otherwise on the validity or legal enforceability of a netting arrangement of any payment system which is not subject to this chapter.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="iddd20efb0-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06">(<ref href="/us/pl/102/242/tIV/s406">Pub. L. 102–242, title IV, § 406</ref>, <date date="1991-12-19">Dec. 19, 1991</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/105/2375">105 Stat. 2375</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
